            <div class="content">
                <h4 class="ttitle">JONGLE'LIVRE</h4>
                <p>
                    Coming to JONGLE'LIVRE, you will easily find the books you want as well as the latest and hottest books in the world.
                    The bookstore currently has more than 100,000 books of different genres.
                    From history books to science books, from domestic literature to foreign literature and countless books from other topics such as comics, novels,... you can choose and explore.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Our primary mission is to bring you good books at reasonable prices.
                    Over the years, JONGLE'LIVRE has had a definite place in the hearts of every book lover. JONGLE'LIVRE is always a prestigious place to be remembered by everyone.
                    Although we are small in size, we are always ready to support you on your way to finding knowledge.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Your love and support will be a great motivation for JONGLE'LIVRE to develop more and more.
                </p>

                <h4 class="ttitle">Main service</h4>
                <p>
                <li>Helps you to quickly and accurately search for book information.</li>
                <li>Nationwide delivery, free shipping with orders over 500,000 VND</li>
                <li>You can order books through the website. If you want to see directly or get the book from the warehouse, please make an appointment in advance. </li>
                </p>

                <h4 class="ttitle">A few words</h4>
                <p>
                <li>JONGLE'LIVRE has been our passion since college years.
                    With all the passion for books, our team founded JONGLE'LIVRE to spread this passion to everyone. 
                    Hopefully JONGLE'LIVRE will become a common home, or an interesting stop on everyone's way to discover the world of books.
                </li>
                <li>We always look forward to everyone's feedback so that we can further improve and develop.</li>
                <li>All comments please contact us by email: <a href="#">jonglelivre@gmail.com</a></li>
                </p>
            </div>
